---
// Icon wrapper component is inlined below
---

<div class="container mx-auto">
  <div
    class="mx-auto text-6xl font-black tracking-tight py-4 text-center text-purple-600"
  >
    Why beampipe?
  </div>

  <div class="flex flex-wrap">
    <!-- Light-weight tracking -->
    <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 p-4 md:p-8">
      <div class="flex flex-row items-start">
        <div class="flex pr-4">
          <div
            class="text-white bg-purple-600 rounded-lg shadow-lg p-2 m-auto w-12 h-12 flex"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-6 h-6 m-auto"
              viewBox="0 0 640 512"
              fill="currentColor"
              ><path
                d="M392.8 1.2c-17-4.9-34.7 5-39.6 22l-128 448c-4.9 17 5 34.7 22 39.6s34.7-5 39.6-22l128-448c4.9-17-5-34.7-22-39.6zm80.6 120.1c-12.5 12.5-12.5 32.8 0 45.3L562.7 256l-89.4 89.4c-12.5 12.5-12.5 32.8 0 45.3s32.8 12.5 45.3 0l112-112c12.5-12.5 12.5-32.8 0-45.3l-112-112c-12.5-12.5-32.8-12.5-45.3 0zm-306.7 0c-12.5-12.5-32.8-12.5-45.3 0l-112 112c-12.5 12.5-12.5 32.8 0 45.3l112 112c12.5 12.5 32.8 12.5 45.3 0s12.5-32.8 0-45.3L77.3 256l89.4-89.4c12.5-12.5 12.5-32.8 0-45.3z"
              ></path></svg
            >
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-lg font-bold">Light-weight tracking script.</div>
          <p>
            Our tracker script is <b>tiny</b>. This means a faster loading page
            and happier users.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4">
            Setup is easy with just a single snippet to add to your site.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Privacy-focussed -->
    <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 p-4 md:p-8">
      <div class="flex flex-row items-start">
        <div class="flex pr-4">
          <div
            class="text-white bg-purple-600 rounded-lg shadow-lg p-2 m-auto w-12 h-12 flex"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-6 h-6 m-auto"
              viewBox="0 0 512 512"
              fill="currentColor"
              ><path
                d="M257.5 27.6c-.8-5.4-4.9-9.8-10.3-10.6c-22.1-3.1-44.6 .9-64.4 11.4l-74 39.5C89.1 78.4 73.2 94.9 63.4 115L26.7 190.6c-9.8 20.1-13 42.9-9.1 64.9l14.5 82.8c3.9 22.1 14.6 42.3 30.7 57.9l60.3 58.4c16.1 15.6 36.6 25.6 58.7 28.7l83 11.7c22.1 3.1 44.6-.9 64.4-11.4l74-39.5c19.7-10.5 35.6-27 45.4-47.2l36.7-75.5c9.8-20.1 13-42.9 9.1-64.9l-14.6-82.8c-3.9-22.1-14.6-42.3-30.7-57.9L369.8 51.5c-16.1-15.6-36.6-25.6-58.7-28.7L257.5 27.6zM184 224a32 32 0 1 1 64 0 32 32 0 1 1-64 0zm128-32a32 32 0 1 1 0 64 32 32 0 1 1 0-64zM176 352a32 32 0 1 1 64 0 32 32 0 1 1-64 0zm160-32a32 32 0 1 1 0 64 32 32 0 1 1 0-64z"
              ></path></svg
            >
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-lg font-bold">Privacy-focussed. No cookies.</div>
          <p>
            We do not use cookies or other personal identifiers. Our service is
            compliant with GDPR, PECR, CCPA.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4">
            Save yourself data compliance headaches without sacrificing
            insights.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Own your data -->
    <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 p-4 md:p-8">
      <div class="flex flex-row items-start">
        <div class="flex pr-4">
          <div
            class="text-white bg-purple-600 rounded-lg shadow-lg p-2 m-auto w-12 h-12 flex"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-6 h-6 m-auto"
              viewBox="0 0 576 512"
              fill="currentColor"
              ><path
                d="M0 80C0 53.5 21.5 32 48 32h96c26.5 0 48 21.5 48 48V96H384V80c0-26.5 21.5-48 48-48h96c26.5 0 48 21.5 48 48v96c0 26.5-21.5 48-48 48H432c-26.5 0-48-21.5-48-48V160H192v16c0 26.5-21.5 48-48 48H48c-26.5 0-48-21.5-48-48V80zM48 336c0-26.5 21.5-48 48-48h96c26.5 0 48 21.5 48 48v16H384V336c0-26.5 21.5-48 48-48h96c26.5 0 48 21.5 48 48v96c0 26.5-21.5 48-48 48H432c-26.5 0-48-21.5-48-48V416H192v16c0 26.5-21.5 48-48 48H48c-26.5 0-48-21.5-48-48V336z"
              ></path></svg
            >
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-lg font-bold">Own your data.</div>
          <p>
            Unlike Google Analytics, <b>you</b> maintain control over your analytics
            data.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4">
            Export to <b>CSV</b> or use our <b>GraphQL API</b> to filter and fetch
            your data on demand.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Free for small sites -->
    <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 p-4 md:p-8">
      <div class="flex flex-row items-start">
        <div class="flex pr-4">
          <div
            class="text-white bg-purple-600 rounded-lg shadow-lg p-2 m-auto w-12 h-12 flex"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-6 h-6 m-auto"
              viewBox="0 0 320 512"
              fill="currentColor"
              ><path
                d="M160 0c17.7 0 32 14.3 32 32V67.7c1.6 .2 3.1 .4 4.7 .7c.4 .1 .7 .1 1.1 .2l48 8.8c17.4 3.2 28.9 19.9 25.7 37.2s-19.9 28.9-37.2 25.7l-47.5-8.7c-31.3-4.6-58.9-1.5-78.3 6.2s-27.2 18.3-29 28.1c-2 10.7-.5 16.7 1.2 20.4c1.8 3.9 5.5 8.3 12.8 13.2c16.3 10.7 41.3 17.7 73.7 26.3l2.9 .8c28.6 7.6 63.6 16.8 89.6 33.8c14.2 9.3 27.6 21.9 35.9 39.5c8.5 17.9 10.3 37.9 6.4 59.2c-6.9 38-33.1 63.4-65.6 76.7c-13.7 5.6-28.6 9.2-44.4 11V480c0 17.7-14.3 32-32 32s-32-14.3-32-32V445.1c-.4-.1-.9-.1-1.3-.2l-.2 0 0 0c-24.4-3.8-64.5-14.3-91.5-26.3c-16.1-7.2-23.4-26-16.2-42.2s26-23.4 42.2-16.2c20.9 9.3 55.3 18.5 75.2 21.6c31.9 4.7 58.2 2 76-5.3c16.9-6.9 24.6-16.9 26.8-28.9c1.9-10.6 .4-16.7-1.3-20.4c-1.9-4-5.6-8.4-13-13.3c-16.4-10.7-41.5-17.7-74-26.3l-2.8-.7c-28.5-7.6-63.5-16.8-89.4-33.9c-14.3-9.4-27.5-22.1-35.7-39.7C13.1 235.3 11.4 215.4 15.2 194c7-38.5 33.5-64.3 66.2-77.6c14.5-5.9 30.2-9.6 46.6-11.4V32c0-17.7 14.3-32 32-32z"
              ></path></svg
            >
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-lg font-bold">Free for small sites.</div>
          <p>
            We think privacy-friendly analytics should be available to <b
              >everyone</b
            >. Our free tier for small sites includes up to 10k page views per
            month.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4">
            If you are lucky enough to see a spike in traffic putting you over
            the limit, we won&apos;t cut you off.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
